Class AbstractCachingDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.data.SeismicDataSource
      • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.data.AbstractCachingDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RsamSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachedDataSource, FileDataSource

    public abstract class AbstractCachingDataSource
extends SeismicDataSource
implements RsamSource
    An implementation of SeismicDataSource which caches data that passes through it. Requires another SeismicDataSource to provide data Mostly build with Dan's code pulled from CachedDataSource
    Author:
    Tom Parker
